---
description: Repository architecture decisions
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use the existing monorepo layout.
- Keep shared types and policy logic in `packages/domain`.
- Keep UI code in `apps/web`.
- Keep HTTP endpoints and orchestration in `apps/api`.
- Avoid circular dependencies between apps and packages.
- New domain logic should be framework-agnostic when possible.
- Add small vertical slices instead of giant rewrites.
- Prefer explicit types over implicit `any`.
